\item Rows \eqn{1 \dots N}: All patients assuming \eqn{y_{prev} = \text{State } 1}
\item Rows \eqn{(N+1) \dots 2N}: All patients assuming \eqn{y_{prev} = \text{State } 2}
\item ... and so on.
