The probability of being in state \eqn{k} at time \eqn{t} is updated as:
\deqn{\mathbf{v}_{curr, k} = \sum_{j} (\mathbf{v}_{prev, j} \odot \mathbf{M}_{trans, j \to k})}
where \eqn{\odot} denotes element-wise multiplication.

